Emulator keys (only work in calculator window for now):
Ctrl-O Open state
Ctrl-S Save state
F11 Reload (or erase memory if no state was loaded)
F12 Save state
Ctrl-Q Quit
F5 Run
F6 Break
Ctrl-Break Break
F7 Step over
F8 Step
F9 Toggle breakpoint

